" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Maisonneuve fracture",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 220px; height: 516px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    This anteroposterior radiograph shows an oblique proximal fibular fracture (arrows). When this results from an ankle injury with concomitant rupture of the tibiofibular syndesmosis, it is referred to as a Maisonneuve fracture.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
